  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that in all this blackness, and all this-- and all this horror, I like to talk about the flower in the desert.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They could be among the enemy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You're supposed to be in [INAUDIBLE], still a human being.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Come out and teach, and tell the people that's supposed to be the patriots, yes, I want them on the picture.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[HEBREW] Human beings.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So that this man, sure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I cannot forgive the Nazis for what they did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I've also learned the lesson that not all the people who are supposed to be good, can be good.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And not all the people who are supposed to be bad are going to be bad.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we should only judge people on their own merit because they can't control their behavior towards other, towards their fellow men.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But they can't control where they come from or what their origin is.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
